<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></div>
<div id="wiki-tab-0-4" style="display:none">
<p>期待ing —— <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/josephjoestar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6159447); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6159447&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="JosephJoestar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6159447)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/josephjoestar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6159447); return false;">JosephJoestar</a></span></p>
<p>悄咪咪的留下一句核電，溜～——<span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lefs" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6896244); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6896244&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="Lefs" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6896244)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lefs" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6896244); return false;">Lefs</a></span></span>改名了，现在是ko no <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-jotaro" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6277235); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6277235&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="the Jotaro" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6277235)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-jotaro" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6277235); return false;">the Jotaro</a></span> da！</p>
<p>恭喜老东西！高产似那啥（）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5526785&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="BruceWu0463" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5526785)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brucewu0463" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5526785); return false;">BruceWu0463</a></span></p>
<p>我敢打赌老东西绝对不会再鸽了）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aplous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6236003); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6236003&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="aplous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6236003)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aplous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6236003); return false;">aplous</a></span><br />
<strong>回复：</strong>一语成谶（反向）</p>
<p>恭喜老&#8230;叫什么好呢？算了不管了，恭喜恭喜！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6150792&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="HigashikataJosuke" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6150792)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;">HigashikataJosuke</a></span><br />
<strong>回复：</strong>叫老爸，仗助崽子（</p>
<p>嘛，老东西只要有上80的文章就给你画人设（——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6114202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="Frozen starry sky" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6114202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/frozen-starry-sky" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6114202); return false;">Frozen starry sky</a></span><br />
<strong>回复：</strong>我允许你重新组织一次语言（</p>
<p>给老东西捧个场，以及一句&quot;老东西NB!&quot;——（一位已经离去的朋友）</p>
<p>人设&#8230;我不太会50多岁，年轻点吧——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wors-obrine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4888797); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4888797&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="WOrs Obrine" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4888797)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wors-obrine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4888797); return false;">WOrs Obrine</a></span></p>
<p><em>咕咕咕</em>——变成鸽子的<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5375092&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="RainTree" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5375092)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/raintree" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5375092); return false;">RainTree</a></span></p>
<p>“Joseph博士年轻时在工作中曾因异常现象被传送至一二维宇宙”这句话很好的掩盖了我因为疏忽没看到人设中的“白发”而画错的失误。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fishbone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6127045); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6127045&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="Dr Fishbone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6127045)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-fishbone" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6127045); return false;">Dr Fishbone</a></span></p>
<p>斯巴拉西，留下一句核电，祝你再创辉煌。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/vastrode" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6251754); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6251754&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="Vastrode" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6251754)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/vastrode" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6251754); return false;">Vastrode</a></span><br />
<strong>回复：</strong>然而就没有过辉煌（泪</p>
<p>咕咕咕，咕咕咕！（鸽语翻译：加油啊，老东西！）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xian-yu-bo-shi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6432694); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6432694&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663853" alt="Xian Yu Bo Shi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6432694)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/xian-yu-bo-shi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6432694); return false;">Xian Yu Bo Shi</a></span></p>
</div>
